<%=EndAppModTitleFont%>
<%=EndAppModParaFont%>



<%=AppModParaFont%>
&#149;	Be positive, but businesslike. Limit small talk.<br>
&#149;	Be brief and to the point.<br>
&#149;	Respect the High D leader's time.<br>
&#149;	Be prepared with facts and logic. Don't generalize.<br>
&#149;	Don't make unsupportable statements.<br>
&#149;	Stress results and a sense of urgency.<br>
&#149;	Emphasize logic, not feelings or emotions.<br>
&#149;	Strive to meet deadlines.<br>
&#149;	Respond positively to and comply with controls.<br>
